<section class="pg-section" data-section="About Our Fillers &amp; Injectables">
  <h2 class="pg-h">About Our Fillers &amp; Injectables</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Dermal fillers can help rejuvenate the skin, smoothing fine lines and giving a fuller, more youthful appearance. A dermal filler is a biological or synthetic product such as a hyaluronic acid-based filler that is injected beneath the skin to reduce the look of fine lines and wrinkles. We use a selection of Juvéderm fillers.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Botox &amp; Injectables target one of the underlying causes of frown lines and crow's feet. This happens as repeated muscle contractions from frowning and squinting over the years. Your specialist will inject these muscles with Botox or other injectables to temporarily reduce muscle activity.</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/botox-millburn-nj">Botox</a>
  <p class="pg-text">You will begin to notice a visible smoothing of your crow's feet lines and frown lines between your brows. We use only the most trusted, FDA-approved brands including Botox, ensuring safe and effective results.</p>
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="JUVÉDERM® Fillers">
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/960c78e88976.jpg" alt="Image by George Colledge" width="1440" height="999" loading="lazy" />
  <h2 class="pg-h">JUVÉDERM® Fillers</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">JUVÉDERM® is the #1 selling brand of hyaluronic acid fillers in the United States.  Each product adds volume to a different area of the face — without surgery. All JUVÉDERM® fillers are smooth, crystal-clear gels that are administered by injection.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Different formulations are approved to either volumize cheeks, smooth parentheses lines, smooth vertical lip lines, or plump the lips. The results are subtle and long-lasting.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">JUVÉDERM® VOLLURE™ XC softens moderate to severe lines and wrinkles by adding volume around the area of nose and mouth in adults over the age of 21.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">JUVÉDERM® VOLUMA™ XC is used to add volume to the cheek area to correct volume loss due to age in adults over 21.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">JUVÉDERM® VOLBELLA™ XC adds soft volume to lips and helps with the appearance of vertical lip lines.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">JUVÉDERM® XC smooths moderate to severe lines and wrinkles surrounding the area of nose and mouth.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">JUVÉDERM® Ultra XC adds fullness and plumps up the lips as well as smooths and corrects moderate to severe appearance of lines in adults.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/f6ffb79bbe28.png" alt="Fillers Cheeks.png" width="154" height="154" loading="lazy" />
